title: [FULL] Age of Empires 2 - Conquerors Patch 1.4
description:
Age of Empires II - The Conquerors patched by Abuga

Current version 1.4 Unofficial patch(Userpatch)


-Original soundtrack WORKING!

-Optimized minimap colors for LCD displays

-Increased population limit to 1000 (by increments of 25)

-No snow on maps (That was really annoying!)

-Widescreen resolutions

-Port fowarding support for Multiplayer Games


Just Install and Enjoy!
